    Click    .site-name__link
    Click    \#ohjeita-hakijalle a
    &{res}=    Wait For Response
    Should Be True    ${res.ok}
    Click    .site-name__link
    Get Element Count    \#edit-openid-connect-client-tunnistamo-login    ==    1

